settings.heading: Discover more..
settings.introduction:
The human connection is as important to us as colour, pattern and joy - there isn’t a single artisan that we work with that we haven’t met in person. Here, you
can get to know more about the highly-skilled British and Indian craftspeople and companies we collaborate with, as well as Molly herself and the things that
matter to her.
